# SRS Governance Rule

- Canonical SRS file is `docs/SRS.md`.
- Do not create a new SRS file (new name, duplicate, or versioned copy) unless the user explicitly confirms after being asked again.
- If user requests creating another SRS file, ask a confirmation question first and wait for answer.
- Prefer updating `docs/SRS.md` in place for all SRS changes.
- Keep BRD and SRS terminology aligned (project ownership, tier access, RBAC, trust score).
